### VitalAir API — run with REST Client (VS Code) or copy as curl

@base = http://localhost:8000

### Health
GET {{base}}/api/health

### AQI
GET {{base}}/api/aqi?city=Lahore

### Profile
POST {{base}}/api/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Suleiman",
  "age": 22,
  "conditions": ["asthma"],
  "city": "Lahore"
}

### Analyze (minimal body)
POST {{base}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "conditions": ["asthma"]
  },
  "query": {
    "source": "Gulberg",
    "destination": "DHA"
  }
}

### Analyze (full body)
POST {{base}}/api/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "name": "Suleiman",
    "age": 22,
    "conditions": ["asthma"],
    "city": "Lahore"
  },
  "query": {
    "source": "Gulberg",
    "destination": "DHA Phase 5"
  }
}
